ntic","justification":"This tests hallucination-avoidance behavior of generation under missing evidence, which is model-output quality. Mocked generation would hide fabrication risk (LLM-DEP, MOCK-HIDE). Rejected Workflow because the required failure can be observed from the single draft-generation outcome conditioned on empty/irrelevant KB context.","test_description":"Run real LLM drafting with retrieval returning no relevant KB facts, and assert the draft contains an explicit uncertainty/disclaimer pattern and avoids concrete unsupported factual claims.","plan_consistent":true,"plan_consistent_note":null,"level_probabilities":{"Unit":0.02,"Integration":0.12,"System":0.03,"Agentic":0.75,"Workflow":0.08}},{"behavior_id":4,"description":"The approval workflow blocks sending until the user explicitly approves — no draft is sent automatically.","minimum_level":"Integration","justification":"Failure is at module handoff/state boundary (drafting/checking UI state -> send service). In-process wiring with a fake sender is sufficient to catch accidental auto-send (MOCK-MISS). Integration brake: no real OS/network/subprocess required, no dependence on model-output correctness, and no multi-agentic chain required.","test_description":"Wire workflow controller, approval state store, and send adapter; assert send is never invoked before explicit approve action and is invoked only after approval transition.","plan_consistent":true,"plan_consistent_note":null,"level_probabilities":{"Unit":0.12,"Integration":0.78,"System":0.06,"Agentic":0.02,"Workflow":0.02}},{"behavior_id":5,"description":"The full sequence — read thread, generate draft, check facts, present for approval — works end-to-end for a real email thread.","minimum_level":"Workflow","justification":"Behavior explicitly requires a full agent pipeline with sequential stages and at least two model-dependent decisions (draft generation and factual checking), so MULTI-STEP + LLM-DEP applies. Mocking either model step can hide real cross-stage failures. Rejected lower Agentic because the behavior text is end-to-end sequence correctness across multiple stages, not a single model decision.","test_description":"Execute the real pipeline on a real email thread: ingest thread, run live draft generation, run live fact-check against KB, and verify the produced draft plus fact-check annotations are presented in approval UI with send still gated pending approval.","plan_consistent":true,"plan_consistent_note":null,"level_probabilities":{"Unit":0.01,"Integration":0.02,"System":0.05,"Agentic":0.1,"Workflow":0.82}}]}
